Operators
-----------

Arithmetic +,-,*,/,%
Relational  >,<,>=,<=,==,!=
logical &&, ||, !
NO increment,decrement (++, --)
bitvise - &,|, ^,>>,<<,~

Ternary operator - not java style scala style straight forward

Scala supports operator overloading

Iterative
--------

   while 
   for

   NO- do while

Conditional

   if else if else

Selection statements

    no switch
    
    pattern matching technique as an alternative
